{"type":"answer","id":18431,"parentType":"question","parentId":4085,"uid":2356,"contents":"参见1950年-1980年代的中国大陆以及目前朝鲜境内的朝鲜公民。<br>\n<br>\n在国门封闭的情况下，要不从云南坐着摩托车，花200块钱偷渡出境到缅甸的佤邦赶紧跑路，要不想方设法动用关系弄到一本大陆护照和某国签证，或者某岛国投资移民护照，赶紧跑路吧。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181101/1541070072864795.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181101/1541070072864795.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181101/1541070072864795.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n这是坠吼的绝招！<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181101/1541069666782107.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181101/1541069666782107.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181101/1541069666782107.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n快速移民护照：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181101/1541069950811575.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181101/1541069950811575.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181101/1541069950811575.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181101/1541069811905043.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181101/1541069811905043.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181101/1541069811905043.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181101/1541069870644236.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181101/1541069870644236.jpg\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181101/1541069870644236.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n千万不要拿到如下了护照：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20181101/1541069892282111.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><